%F A060540 T(n,k) = (n*k)!/(k!^n*n!) = T(n-1,k)*A060543(n,k) = A060538(n,k)/k!.
%F A060540 T(n,k) = Product_{j=2..n} binomial(j*k-1,k-1). - _M. F. Hasler_, Aug 22 2014
